tail">Retail</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/about-us/a-sustainable-approach">A sustainable approach</a><ul class="sub-menu"><li><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/about-us/a-sustainable-approach/international-principles">International principles</a></li><li><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/about-us/a-sustainable-approach/responsible-products-and-services">Responsible products and services</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/about-us/our-history">Our history</a></li><li><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/about-us/the-mondadori-brand">The Mondadori brand</a></li><li><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/about-us/our-headquarters">Our headquarters</a></li></ul><div class="menu-highlight"> <article class="article-preview"> <figure><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/about-us/our-headquarters"><img width="380" height="556" src="http://static.mondadori.it/content/uploads/2016/07/rh1663-54-380x556.jpg?8d48fe" class="img-responsive SI-img-vertical" alt="Palazzo Niemeyer" style="width:auto; max-height:232px;" srcset="http://static.mondadori.it/content/uploads/2016/07/rh1663-54-123x180.jpg 123w, http://www.mondadori.it/content/uploads/2016/07/rh1663-54-380x556.jpg 380w, http://www.mondadori.it/content/uploads/2016/07/rh1663-54.jpg 547w" sizes="(max-width: 380px) 85vw, 380px"/></a></figure> <time datetime="2017-04-06 00:00:00">6 Apr 2017 </time><h3 class="clr mid"><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/about-us/our-headquarters">Our headquarters</a></h3><p>Between 1950 and 1965, the number of employees at Mondadori rose from 335 to 3,000 and resulted in the company's decision to construct a new&hellip;</p> </article></div><li data-section="s02" class="menu-item menu-item-s02"> <a href="javascript:void(0);">Our Brands</a><div class="menu-description"><h3 class="clr">Books</h3><p>From the publishing brand that gives its name to the entire Group, up to the brands that recently entered the scope of activities with the acquisition of Rizzoli Libri: there are over 30 publishing houses and relative imprints in the book sector, ranging from literary fiction to non-fiction, from illustrated art to books for children, and from university and school textbooks to leisure and entertainment titles.</p> <a href="http://www.mondadori.com/our-brands/books" class="btn bg">continue</a></div><ul id="menu-our-brands" class="sub-menu"><li><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/our-brands/books">Books</a></li><li><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/our-brands/magazines-and-digital">Magazines and digital</a></li><li><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/our-brands/retail">Retail</a></li></ul><div class="menu-highlight"> <article class="article-preview"> <figure><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/media-room/news-and-press-releases/year-2017/paolo-cognetti-wins-the-2017-premio-strega-2017-with-le-otto-montagne"><img width="380" height="567" src="http://static.mondadori.it/content/uploads/2017/07/Cognetti-A3-380x567.jpg?8d48fe" class="img-responsive SI-img-vertical" alt="Cognetti cover" style="width:auto; max-height:232px;" srcset="http://static.mondadori.it/content/uploads/2017/07/Cognetti-A3-768x1146.jpg 768w, http://www.mondadori.it/content/uploads/2017/07/Cognetti-A3-380x567.jpg 380w, http://www.mondadori.it/content/uploads/2017/07/Cognetti-A3-570x851.jpg 570w, http://www.mondadori.it/content/uploads/2017/07/Cognetti-A3-700x1045.jpg 700w, http://www.mondadori.it/content/uploads/2017/07/Cognetti-A3-850x1268.jpg 850w" sizes="(max-width: 380px) 85vw, 380px"/></a></figure> <time datetime="2017-07-13 00:00:00">13 Jul 2017 </time><h3 class="clr mid"><a href="http://www.mondadori.com/media-room/news-and-press-releases/year-2017/paolo-cognetti-wins-the-2017-premio-strega-2017-with-le-otto-montagne">Paolo Cognetti wins the 2017 Premio Strega 2017 with “Le otto montagne”</a></h3><p>On Thursday 6 July, in the captivating space of the Ninfeo of the Villa Giulia in Rome, Paolo Cognetti won the 71st Premio Strega with his&hellip;</p> </article></div><li