receives a Randstad Employer Brand 2017 award</a></h3><p>The Mondadori Group is among the companies who have won the Randstad Employer Brand 2017, the award given by Randstad - the world’s second largest&hellip;</p> </article></div></ul></div> </nav><form method="get" class="search-form" data-attr-action="/search/" role="search" action="/search/"><div class="form-group"> <span class="alert">Period</span> <input id="search-string" name="s" type="text" class="typeahead form-control" placeholder="What are you looking for?"></div> <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default"><span class="icon-search"></span><span class="icon-close"></span></button></form> <a class="menu-toggle visible-xs js-xs-menu-toggle"><span class="icon-menu"></span></a></div><div id="submenu1-container"></div> </header><div id="content"> <article><div class="js-sticky-header line"><div class="hidden-xs container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-9 col-lg-12"><ol class="breadcrumb"><li><a href="http://www.mondadori.it">Home</a></li><li class="active"> Privacy Policy</li></ol></div></div></div></div><header class="article-header"><div class="container"><h1 class="article-subheading auto_SI_title clr">Privacy Policy</h1></div></header><div id="pl-15638"><header class="article-header"><div class="panel-grid" id="pg-15638-0-SI"><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-15638-0-0-SI">&nbsp;</div></div> </header><div class="container"><div class="entry socialvertical js-sticky_parent"><div class="clearfix"><ul class="share js-sticky_column share-buttons"><li><a class="bg" href="javascript: void(0);" data-attr-href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Privacy Policy&url=http://www.mondadori.com/privacy-policy-eng&via=mondadori"><span class="icon-twitter"></span></a></li><li><a class="bg" href="javascript: void(0);" data-attr-href="https://www.facebook.com/dialog/share?app_id=688832651190210&display=popup&redirect_uri=http://www.mondadori.com/privacy-policy-eng&href=http://www.mondadori.com/privacy-policy-